  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Arter</strong> is a <i>puzzle/platform</i> game inspired by the Mario vs Donkey Kong, with an emphasis on picking up the key and taking it to the door while solving puzzles. Featuring pixel art inspired by 16-bit games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/0764f7c6b7c9d3a387227d0a481daac4.poster.avif?t=1763006926\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/0764f7c6b7c9d3a387227d0a481daac4.webm?t=1763006926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, throw objects, use switches, dodge traps, defeat enemies, and more to overcome obstacles in your path. Search for the key to open the door to the next level and clear your way until you face the boss of each world to collect all the Domino Relics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/1b3a28a547fdbb652b1ef5edb8a427a1.avif?t=1763006926\" width=616 height=52 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve various puzzles across <strong>five</strong> different worlds, each featuring multiple stages.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/347e129f2150ed1b65f6bd0851be0ec0.poster.avif?t=1763006926\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/347e129f2150ed1b65f6bd0851be0ec0.webm?t=1763006926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a powerful boss at the end of every world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/d68873590d4cac2dd93a567381f0c614.poster.avif?t=1763006926\" width=620 height=68 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/d68873590d4cac2dd93a567381f0c614.webm?t=1763006926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recover the Domino Relics stolen by the Dark Wizard by solving the most challenging puzzles, facing enemies, collecting gifts, and discovering the best way for Arter to take the key to the door in this platform/puzzle game.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Arter</strong> is a <i>puzzle/platform</i> game inspired by the Mario vs Donkey Kong, with an emphasis on picking up the key and taking it to the door while solving puzzles. Featuring pixel art inspired by 16-bit games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/0764f7c6b7c9d3a387227d0a481daac4.poster.avif?t=1763006926\" width=600 height=210 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/0764f7c6b7c9d3a387227d0a481daac4.webm?t=1763006926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Jump, throw objects, use switches, dodge traps, defeat enemies, and more to overcome obstacles in your path. Search for the key to open the door to the next level and clear your way until you face the boss of each world to collect all the Domino Relics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/1b3a28a547fdbb652b1ef5edb8a427a1.avif?t=1763006926\" width=616 height=52 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve various puzzles across <strong>five</strong> different worlds, each featuring multiple stages.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/347e129f2150ed1b65f6bd0851be0ec0.poster.avif?t=1763006926\" width=600 height=96 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/347e129f2150ed1b65f6bd0851be0ec0.webm?t=1763006926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face a powerful boss at the end of every world.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/d68873590d4cac2dd93a567381f0c614.poster.avif?t=1763006926\" width=620 height=68 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2136060/extras/d68873590d4cac2dd93a567381f0c614.webm?t=1763006926\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recover the Domino Relics stolen by the Dark Wizard by solving the most challenging puzzles, facing enemies, collecting gifts, and discovering the best way for Arter to take the key to the door in this platform/puzzle game.</p>",
